      <para az:dropcap="true" az:dropcapcolor="#fddd66" az:dropcapbackgroundcolor="#71aaa4" az:dropcapfileref="../illustrations/Capitals/T-yellow2.png">The inventor Zangemann is world-famous and immensely rich. Adults and children alike love his fabulous technical inventions. But one day there is a problem: the children's electronic skateboards no longer work properly. What’s going on? The curious girl Ada sees through what is going on. Together with her friends, she experiments with hardware and software, and the children forge a plan: Zangemann can no longer be the only one in control of the devices!</para>
