  <appendix xml:id="ch18">
    <info>
      <!-- TODO: deal with multi-line title. Check if this modelling works. -->
      <title>About the Author</title>
      <subtitle>Matthias Kirschner</subtitle>
      <titleabbrev>About the Author - Matthias Kirschner</titleabbrev>
    </info>
    <section az:pagenum="52">
      <anchor az:slidenum="10"/>
      <mediaobject xml:id="img-ada-p52">
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="../illustrations/en/ada-p52.png"/>
        </imageobject>
        <alt>Close-up of Matthias smiling, waving with one hand, and wearing a headset. Matthias has short hair and a little beard.</alt>
      </mediaobject>
      <para>Matthias was fascinated by computers and software as a child. He had an internet connection early, through which he learned a lot. Children have a right to take their future into their own hands. Therefore, Matthias is committed to the goal that all humans can use software in a self-determined way. He also wants to build an electric skateboard with Free Software.</para>
    </section>
  </appendix>
  <appendix xml:id="ch19">
