      <subtitle>Sandra Brandstätter</subtitle>
      <titleabbrev>About the Illustrator - Sandra Brandstätter</titleabbrev>
    </info>
    <section az:pagenum="53">
      <anchor az:slidenum="11"/>
      <mediaobject xml:id="img-ada-p53">
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="../illustrations/en/ada-p53.png"/>
        </imageobject>
        <alt>Sandra smiling with a pencil in her hand in front of her chin. She has earphones with an integrated microphone. Sandra has short hair and glasses.</alt>
      </mediaobject>
      <para>Sandra has always liked crafting with scissors, pliers, glue, wire, fabric, and paper. Today she works as an illustrator, comic author, and character designer for animated films and series, such as the German public television series Trudes Tier. On an ice-cream machine, Sandra would pick a creamy rainbow ice cream with lemon cucumber flavor and a lot of sprinkles.</para>
