  <appendix xml:id="ch20">
    <info>
      <!-- TODO: this title abbreviation is incorrect compared to titles -->
      <!-- <title>Website for the book and license</title> -->
      <title>Website for the book</title>
    </info>
    <section az:pagenum="54">
      <para>The Free Software Foundation Europe e.V. is a nonprofit association that empowers people to control technology. Software affects all areas of our life. That is why it is important that this technology gives us freedom instead of restricting us. Free Software (also called Open Source) gives everyone the right to use, study, share, and improve programs. Therefore, Free Software strengthens basic rights such as freedom of expression, freedom of the press, and the right to privacy.</para>
      <!-- TODO: Consider a newline to prevent wrapping -->
      <para>On the web page of the book, you will find more information and resources: <link xlink:href="https://ada.fsfe.org">https://ada.fsfe.org</link>.</para>
    </section>
  </appendix>
